## Project Overview

<!-- 2–3 sentences. What is this project? What stage is it at?
The agent uses this to calibrate its assumptions about what matters and what
"good output" looks like. A paper at the writing stage needs different help
than a codebase at the debugging stage.

Example (ML paper): "NeurIPS 2026 submission on causal representation learning.
Experiments complete. Currently writing the results section and preparing camera-ready."

Example (software tool): "Python library for automated BibTeX verification.
Public API stable. Currently adding a CLI and writing documentation." -->

[2–3 sentences describing what this project is and what stage it is at.]

